Name: Angel Wings
Description:
Activates outfit: Angel Wings - Backwear

You can also take it to Callista in the Meowlux Member Store on the 2nd floor of the mall near the Development Bureau for recycling and exchange for a certain amount of Meowlux Premium Cards (Bound).
